<h1>Welcome!</h1>

<p>
  Hi <%= @user.name %>, welcome to Danebook!
</p>

<p>
  Here are some things you can do to get started:
  <ul>
    <li>
    Fill out your <%= link_to "profile", user_url(@user.id) %> so that others can learn more about you!
    </li>
    <li>
      Go to your <%= link_to "timeline", user_posts_url(@user.id) %> and write your first post!
    </li>
    <li>
      Go to you <%= link_to "photos", user_photos_url(@user.id) %> and upload some pictures. You can also choose your profile and cover photos here.
    </li>
  </ul>
</p>
